                     <interp inst="t18150405-40-off215" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18150405-40-victim408" type="victimName">
                           Alexander 
                           Sinclair
                        <interp inst="t18150405-40-victim408" type="surname" value="Sinclair"></interp>
