                  , about the hour of one in the night of the <rs id="t18150405-40-cd216" type="crimeDate">13th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150405-40-off215 t18150405-40-cd216"></join>, and stealing therein, nine elephants teeth, value 110 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18150405-40-victim410" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Sinclair
